**Hosting**: Cloud infrastructure on [platform]

This stack ensures performance, security, and maintainability.` },
        { id: 'pricing', type: 'pricing', title: 'Investment', showTotal: true, items: [
          { id: 'p1', name: 'Phase 1: Foundation', description: 'Architecture, database design, core infrastructure', quantity: 1, unitPrice: 8000, optional: false, selected: true },
          { id: 'p2', name: 'Phase 2: Core Features', description: 'Primary functionality development', quantity: 1, unitPrice: 15000, optional: false, selected: true },
          { id: 'p3', name: 'Phase 3: Polish & Launch', description: 'UI refinement, testing, production deployment', quantity: 1, unitPrice: 5000, optional: false, selected: true },
          { id: 'p4', name: 'Training & Documentation', description: 'User training and technical documentation', quantity: 1, unitPrice: 2000, optional: true, selected: false },
          { id: 'p5', name: 'Monthly Support', description: 'Ongoing maintenance and support hours', quantity: 1, unitPrice: 800, optional: true, selected: false },
        ]},
        { id: 'terms', type: 'section', title: 'Terms', content: `Timeline: [X weeks] from project kickoff

